  "summary": "AI-powered university chatbot for VIT-AP students using Retrieval-Augmented Generation, semantic retrieval, local LLMs, and vector databases for contextual campus assistance.",
  "description": "Built an AI-powered university assistant designed specifically for VIT-AP students to simplify access to campus-related information, academic guidance, fresher onboarding support, university procedures, and contextual query answering. The system uses Retrieval-Augmented Generation pipelines with semantic retrieval workflows powered by ChromaDB and local LLM inference using Ollama. Designed to provide contextual, low-latency, privacy-focused AI assistance for college students.",
  "problem_statement": "Freshers and students often struggle to find accurate and contextual university-related information such as academic procedures, departments, onboarding guidance, and campus workflows. Traditional search systems lack contextual understanding and semantic retrieval capabilities.",
  "solution": "Developed a semantic AI assistant capable of retrieving contextual university information using vector embeddings, Retrieval-Augmented Generation, local LLM orchestration, and semantic search pipelines.",
